Core based on: 		Operserv 2.36 by Fox_Muld 
Auth module based on:	QmOd by EZ_Target
Anything else is coded by Wiedi


Howto Install:

 $ make

Howto Configure:

 $ $EDITOR xevres.conf
 $ $EDITOR ~/lib/ircd.conf

 Do not forget to add the U line on all servers:

  U:xevres.xchannel.org.org:X:*

Howto Setup:
 
 $ ./Xevres

 Connect to your ircd and do (as an oper):
 
 /msg X create
 /msg X login <username> <passwort>
 /msg X createdb_auth
 /msg X createdb_chan

Well done, now everything should work!

If you have problems: join #xchannel on irc.xchannel.org
